<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٢٥٣ - وَقَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3817">أَبُو مَعْمَرٍ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4076">عَبْدُ الْوَارِثِ: </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">أَيُّوبُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2343">سَعِيدِ بْنِ جُبَيْرٍ، </a>عَنِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنِ عُمَرَ </a>قَالَ: <span class="c2">«حُسِبَتْ عَلَيَّ بِتَطْلِيقَةٍ»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>